{
  "stem": "11642.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They left him a little bit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my-- and then they came for me, a little bit later, to transfer me to jail.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This I also won't forget.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was passing by, going to the station, and my father was shoveling the snow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My father knew where they going take me because this was the time when he knew they go and transfer me to jail, with two Germans and one Jewish person who was with me.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I passed by.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I said to that Jewish person, let me give a hug, a kiss my father.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This, he said, you cannot do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You just can close by him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And while I was close by, my father picked up his hat and he went like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I knew exactly what he meant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "No matter what's going happen to you, never say who gave you this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They took me to jail.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The name of the place was Wadowice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was 1941, something like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I came into jail, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I came-- this was on a Friday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they kept me in a Jewish family over Saturday, also because they knew who I am.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Sunday morning, I rang the bell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And their doorman opened and he let me into jail.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They gave me-- the job what I had was a good job, I have to say, because I was working in a garden from fruit-- picking fruit.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- and since I knew already a little bit of German, because I took in school, and Polish, so I was translating to the Polish women to the Germans what-- so it wasn't too bad.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "While I was there, maybe three months later, somebody came also from our own town.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
